# Frontend Environment Variables (Updated for Backend Proxy Architecture)

# Backend API URL
# In development: http://localhost:5000
# In production: https://your-backend-domain.com
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT MIGRATION NOTE:
# The frontend NO LONGER calls Gemini API directly!
# All API calls go through the backend proxy:
# - Chat requests → /api/chat
# - Image analysis → /api/analyze  
# - Location data → /api/location
#
# The backend uses GEMINI_API_KEY from its own .env file
# This is more secure and prevents rate limiting issues